This is installation steps for terraform and AWS CLI
Prerequiste :
we need to have python 2.7 or above version
Step1:
Install AWS cli package from the below web page
https://docs.aws.amazon.com/cli/latest/userguide/install-macos.html
Step2:
Install Terraform package in the required system

https://www.terraform.io/downloads.html
https://www.terraform.io/docs/configuration-0-11/interpolation.html
